Thanks for downloading Socialtext Open.

== Requirements==

You will need to have root or sudo on your server to install Socialtext Open.

Hardware, software, and operating system requirements are here:

   http://www.socialtext.net/open/index.cgi?socialtext_open_requirements

== How to Install ==

Installation directions are in the INSTALL file.  It's an overview, and you may need to refer to the detailed walkthroughs in /docs. 

== Online Resources and Help ==

There are a number of online resources for Socialtext Open.

http://www.socialtext.net/open/
    The home wiki workspace for all open source related to Socialtext,
    including the Socialtext Open product you've just downloaded.

http://sourceforge.net/projects/socialtext
    SourceForge is the host of the downloads and source code repository for Socialtext Open.

http://www.socialtext.net/exchange
     A wiki for users and Socialtext customers.

If all else fails, or you have other questions about Socialtext Open,
you can also write to socialtext-user@lists.socialtext.net.


